{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_ascln_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_ascln_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"同行人","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"特蕾西娅遇刺后，一群不再与罗德岛同行的萨卡兹在罗德岛必经的航道上设伏，意欲阻截，而阿斯卡纶找上了他们。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_ascln_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["阿斯卡纶","特雷西斯","巴别塔成员","？？？","细盐","凯尔希"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_bg_49_g4_kazdelstreet_shabby.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$ponder_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_ponder_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"text","text":"1072年秋","id":9},{"type":"dialog","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":11},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":12},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","posfrom":"-200,0","posto":"0,0","id":13},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":14},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_wind","volume":"1","id":15},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":16},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":17},{"type":"charslot","id":18},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":19},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":20},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_bldwhoosh","id":21},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#4$1","posfrom":"50,0","posto":"250,0","duration":"0.3","id":22},{"type":"delay","time":"0.1","id":23},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.3","id":24},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":25},{"type":"charslot","id":26},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.01","block":"true","id":27},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.2","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"50","randomness":"90","fadeout":"false","block":"false","id":28},{"type":"playsound","key":"$swordtsing4","id":29},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.3","block":"false","id":30},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_bg_49_g4_kazdelstreet_shabby.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":31},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_swordy","id":32},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":33},{"type":"text","text":"刺客从阴影中跃出，一柄断剑几乎是贴着特雷西斯的前胸掠过。他侧身，出手，佩剑已经横在了刺客的脖颈上。","id":34},{"type":"dialog","id":35},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":36},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":37},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":38},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":40,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_1301_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"日影刚好在此时完全倾斜过来，将街道遮住。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"......你一直在等待这一刻。","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"这样确实能最大化发挥你的优势，隐藏身形，接近敌人。但在昼夜交替的特殊时刻，你的敌人对环境变化的感知也会更敏感。","id":44,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"好，知道了。","id":46,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_1301_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"整个下午，我一共出手了七次，但一次都没能得手。","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_1301_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"换一个对手，你早就成功了。","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"你割断了我胸前的绑带......用这柄曾经被我斩断的长剑。","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"今天就到这里，明天继续。","id":53,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5c/Avg_avg_npc_1301_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"昨天，两个喝醉的佣兵闯进了我们的办公地点，他们扔下了一个酒壶，里面是活性化的源石粉尘。","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_1301_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"当时，殿下正在大厅给两个孩子包扎伤口。","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_1301_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"那不是意外。","id":59,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_1301_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"我已经知道，我已经处理。","id":61,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"类似的事情，越来越多。","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_1301_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"军事委员会......你保护不了殿下和巴别塔？你是真的没有办法，还是在纵容他们？","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_1301_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"这件事，不需要你来质问我，阿斯卡纶。","id":66,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"什么对萨卡兹更好，我比你更清楚。","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"可是，老师......","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_1301_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"如果真有人对殿下动手，你会出手吗！","id":71,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e2/Avg_avg_npc_1301_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"会。","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"那如果其他人都架着你，逼你对她动手，你会出手吗？","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e2/Avg_avg_npc_1301_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":76},{"type":"text","text":"沉默。","id":77},{"type":"text","text":"但两人的心中各自都有了答案。","id":78},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"这是最后一堂课了，老师。","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/99/Avg_avg_npc_1301_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"我没有想通......但从明天起，我会去殿下身边，守护好她。","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5c/Avg_avg_npc_1301_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1301_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"连带着你本应有的心意一起。","id":84,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9f/Avg_avg_npc_1301_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":85},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":86},{"type":"text","text":"阿斯卡纶不再言语，她弯腰捡起刚刚被特雷西斯打落的断剑，以及散落在一旁，被她视作战利品的断裂绑带。","id":87},{"type":"text","text":"她头也不回地离开。","id":88},{"type":"dialog","id":89},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":90},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"-200,0","duration":"1","afrom":"1","ato":"0","id":91},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":92},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1297_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"......","id":94,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"你选择的只是某个人，而不是那个人脚下的道路。","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"特雷西斯","text":"不知道为何而行，那么你要如何承受失去同行人的痛苦，阿斯卡纶？","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/51/Avg_avg_npc_1297_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":97},{"type":"dialog","id":98},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":99},{"type":"charslot","id":100},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":101},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_bg_bg_coldforest.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":102},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loading_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_sys_loading_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":103,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":104},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":105},{"type":"text","text":"1094年秋","id":106},{"type":"text","text":"卡兹戴尔北部地区","id":107},{"type":"dialog","id":108},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1308_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":109},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":110},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","id":111},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔成员","text":"炸药已经填放好。接下来我就守在这里......","id":113,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔成员","text":"土方子、早霜，船上还有好几个跟我一样熟悉航路的人，要是发现异样，他们会在第一时间让罗德岛转向。","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"巴别塔成员","text":"只剩下一个小时了，我得守在这里，保证炸药能在罗德岛经过这片区域的时候被触发——","id":115,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你放在外围的人都已经死了，细盐。","id":117},{"type":"dialog","id":118},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1308_1#1$1","id":119},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","id":120},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"阿斯卡纶......","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"哈，还是被你找到了。","id":123,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":124},{"type":"charslot","id":125},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":126},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":127},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1308_1#1$1","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"也是，我的武艺和潜行的技术都是你教的，指望躲过你，不现实。","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"说起来，以前我就好奇，不管藏得多么好，都能被你找到，你到底是靠什么精准定位到每个人的？","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"味道？声音？","id":133,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"......总不能是靠哈出来的气吧，这在你看来也是某种“烟”？","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1308_1#1$1","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"*萨卡兹粗口*，还真是！","id":138,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"那就没办法了，我总不能不呼吸。","id":139,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"既然都被你发现了，介意我生堆火吗？入秋了，这荒郊野岭的，冷得很！","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":141},{"type":"charslot","id":142},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_woodcracle","id":143},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":144},{"type":"text","text":"萨卡兹生起了火，风有点大，他用剑拨了拨火堆，火势才起来，哔剥声变大了，声音远远地传开去。","id":145},{"type":"text","text":"阿斯卡纶没有动。","id":146},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"这些烈性源石炸药，制作得很粗糙......","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1308_1#1$1","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"情报到手得有点迟，做得太仓促了。","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"当年离开卡兹戴尔的时候，我万万没想到，先是需要跟你学潜行和动刀子，后来又得学做炸药，和这些我最讨厌的石头打交道。","id":151,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"说真的，这比把野生盐泉旁边的那些粗盐粒提炼成可以吃的细盐可难多了。","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"说起来，当时缺帽檐“细盐”“细盐”地叫我的时候，就应该直接给他一拳让他闭嘴。","id":153,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"这个代号太娇贵了，一听就是吃不了苦的......我好心让大家伙在荒野上执行任务的时候能吃得好点，结果还被取笑。","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"......谁知道后来你也跟着这么叫。","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"顺口。","id":157,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......从这些炸药的体量来看，爆炸范围足以覆盖好几公里。","id":159,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#8$1","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"为了逼停罗德岛，你不惜让这整片区域都受到不可逆的污染？","id":161,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1308_1#1$1","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"......","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#8$1","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"你不应该做这样的事，也不应该是你。","id":165,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"细盐，你的任务是清洗那些叛徒。","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1308_1#1$1","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"殿下遇刺的时候，我们在那个小镇上阻击那些佣兵，我们用最快的速度赶回来......还来得及做的也只有跟你一起清洗那些叛徒。","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"参与了那场刺杀的巴别塔成员，早就被你、被我们杀光了。十几，几十，还是上百？我忘了......","id":169,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"那些不屑于你们现在所做的事的人，已经不会再愿意回到罗德岛......包括我，我成了他们的一分子。","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"“叛徒”？","id":171,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"阿斯卡纶，到底谁才是叛徒？","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1308_1#1$1","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"阿斯卡纶，你应该和那个叫凯尔希的菲林保持着联系，对吧？","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"难道你没有听说吗，他们不会再尝试回到卡兹戴尔，更不会去为特蕾西娅殿下复仇！","id":178,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"才三个月，殿下死后才短短三个月，他们甚至已经在打算彻底扔掉“巴别塔”这个名字......","id":179,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"如今那艘船里还剩下多少萨卡兹？上百？几十？还是十几？","id":180,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"我不关心那艘船和那艘船上的人是不是将来不会再和我们有联系，但我们必须拿回属于萨卡兹、属于卡兹戴尔的东西！","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"那个总待在特蕾西娅殿下身边的小卡特斯，那个新的魔——","id":182,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_1308_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":183},{"type":"charslot","id":184},{"type":"playsound","key":"$knifegore","id":185},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":186},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":187},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":188},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":189},{"type":"text","text":"萨卡兹佣兵看着阿斯卡纶消失在原地，等他反应过来的时候，对方的袖刃已经深深刺进自己的身体，鲜血洇过胸前的布甲。","id":190},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown1","id":191},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"10","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":192},{"type":"text","text":"下一个瞬间，锐利的疼痛才追上他。他跪倒在地，险些将火堆扑灭。","id":193},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"你们的目标是阿米娅。","id":195,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3e/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"这件事，殿下自有她的安排。","id":196,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3e/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"这个词，你不该想，也不该提。","id":197,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3e/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"咕——咳，咳咳......","id":199},{"type":"dialog","id":200},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"当年，咳咳，离开卡兹戴尔，我是在你们的队伍......快消失不见的时候才，决定追上你们......我连行李都没带......","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"我想要的，和殿下在做的事情差不多......让大家的日子能，过得更好一些......","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"咳，我知道殿下的目标，殿下要走的路肯定比我想的要复杂很多......但她走在队伍的前面，我们就，不用去想。","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"但现在......","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"阿斯卡纶，咳，你是离殿下最近的人......你不应该阻止我们，你是最不应该阻止我们的人，应该是你带领我们去这么做......","id":206},{"type":"charslot","id":207},{"type":"text","text":"一口气说了太多的话，萨卡兹剧烈地咳嗽起来，血从喉咙深处涌上来，他的身体止不住地前倾，袖刃被更深地送进胸腔。","id":208},{"type":"text","text":"但阿斯卡纶只是俯身看着他。","id":209},{"type":"text","text":"或许是火堆快灭了，林子里太暗了吧，他总觉得阿斯卡纶的眼睛里有太多阴影，什么都看不清。","id":210},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"还是说，殿下死后，你真的跟其他人说的那样，咳咳，已经没有方向了，已经疯了......","id":212},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":214,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#2$1","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"最后的时间，告诉我，阿米娅的事情，还有多少人知情？","id":216,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"咳咳，已经迟了，阿斯卡纶。","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"我死了，你也阻止不了这场行动......","id":219},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":220},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#6$1","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"——！","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"你刚刚的通讯对象，不是外围那些被我杀死的人。","id":224,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3e/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"有另外一支队伍也在进行同样的行动......","id":225,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3e/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"你在这里，就是为了吸引我的注意力？","id":226,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3e/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"你只有一个人，你没有办法——","id":228},{"type":"dialog","id":229},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":230},{"type":"text","text":"翻涌的血块和最后的话都被堵在了喉头，萨卡兹看见薄幕般的烟雾像是不受控制一般从阿斯卡纶的身体逸出。","id":231},{"type":"text","text":"那些烟雾像是活物，扑灭了火堆，很快融进了幽深的夜色里。","id":232},{"type":"text","text":"通过胸口的袖刃，他感受到了阿斯卡纶的手在颤抖，她的身体像是忽然之间发生了某种“坍塌”，止不住地颤抖......","id":233},{"type":"charslot","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"细盐","text":"......","id":235},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#7$1","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":237,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":238},{"type":"text","text":"生命的最后，萨卡兹在这个他已经熟识多年的刺客脸上，看见了他从未见过的，痛苦。","id":239},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":240},{"type":"dialog","id":241},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":242},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":243},{"type":"charslot","id":244},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":245},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":246},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2b/Avg_bg_49_g14_rhodesdeck_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":247},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":248},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":249,"musicid":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......你终于回来了，阿斯卡纶。","id":251,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":252},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":253},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":254},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":255},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"嗯。","id":257,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"离这里三十公里的两片雷区，Ace他们正在带人清除，罗德岛暂时会停泊在这里。","id":259,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"那两伙人......","id":261,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"一百三十四人。","id":263,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":264},{"type":"text","text":"凯尔希低头，接过阿斯卡纶递来的东西。","id":265},{"type":"text","text":"那是一摞布条，无一例外地别着巴别塔的袖标，它们有的已不完整，有的被血染透，黏腻得根本看不出本来的颜色。","id":266},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"参与了那场刺杀的叛徒，还有那些不该知晓阿米娅身份的人，已经全部清除。","id":268,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你伤得很重，晚一些需要到医疗部接受全面的检查。","id":270,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......你的源石技艺几近自伤，以你目前的情绪状态，我不建议你接下来继续深度使用它。","id":271,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"好。","id":273,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"接下来你打算怎么做？","id":275,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"你召回了我。这些问题，应该我问。","id":277,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"好。","id":279,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"特蕾西娅殿下的尸体？","id":281,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"与刺杀发生几乎同时，罗德岛附近的荒原上出现了赦罪师的身影，这两件事情必然存在关联。罗德岛不会放弃追查。","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"特雷西斯，罗德岛以后怎么看待他？","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"罗德岛已不再是萨卡兹流亡政府，我们也并不具备和军事委员会正面对抗的能力。","id":287,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"矿石病将是今后罗德岛需要处理的主要问题。至于特雷西斯......将是我，你，我们这些少数人需要面对的问题，或者心结。","id":288,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"博士？","id":290,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#14$1","focus":"r","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我知道你对博士仍有怀疑。","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3d/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-14$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"仅从结果来看，特蕾西娅确实选择在最后关头以她的方式保护了博士。现阶段，将博士送往乌萨斯，是最合适的做法。","id":293,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3d/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-14$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......嗯。","id":295,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":296},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"all","id":297},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":298},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"阿斯卡纶，看来你暂时没有问题了。","id":300,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"选择在此时将你召回，是因为罗德岛需要组建一个完全独立运作的机密组织，我叫它“S.W.E.E.P.”——“特别清除协议”。","id":301,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"这件事应该由你来负责。","id":302,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"“S.W.E.E.P.”？","id":304,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"S.W.E.E.P.要做两件事：阻止针对罗德岛的渗透、暗杀和破坏；执行隐秘行动，用上述方式解决问题，和以前一样。","id":306,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"和以前一样......","id":308,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"我并没有守护好殿下。","id":309,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"你希望我留下来，做我没有做到的事情，你希望我为殿下的死赎罪。","id":310,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b3/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"不，阿斯卡纶，这不是赎罪。","id":312,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"巴别塔已经不复存在，但仍有无数双眼睛盯着我们，这艘船仍然举步维艰。","id":314,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"刚刚过去的事情，绝不能在罗德岛再发生。","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你曾经是特雷西斯的学徒，巴别塔的反情报专家，没有人比你更适合这项工作，仅此而已。","id":317,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"而且，你不会是一个人，你也不能是一个人。","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我希望由你担任S.W.E.E.P.的主管。","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿斯卡纶","text":"......","id":321,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_avg_4132_ascln_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你不必马上回答，阿斯卡纶。","id":323,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"在给我任何回复之前，我有一个请求：去见见阿米娅。","id":324,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":325},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":326},{"type":"charslot","id":327},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":328},{"type":"gridbg","imagegroup":"44_g13_afterglow_L1/44_g13_afterglow_R1/44_g13_afterglow_L2/44_g13_afterglow_R2","solidwidth":"1280/1280/1280/1280","solidheight":"720/720/720/720","y":"500","id":329},{"type":"largebgtween","duration":"60","yFrom":"500","yTo":"700","block":"false","id":330},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":331},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":332},{"type":"text","text":"残阳如血。","id":333},{"type":"text","text":"她们最后的交谈在肆意扬起的风沙中被掩去。","id":334},{"type":"text","text":"“这段时间我一直待在她身边，阿米娅已经适应了身体的变化......也不再哭了。”","id":335},{"type":"text","text":"“阿斯卡纶，去见见她。或许你能明白，为什么特蕾西娅最后会选择她......特蕾西娅的道路并未终结。”","id":336},{"type":"text","text":"“或许到时候，你会重新找到归属感，你的袖刃会为了一个更明确的目标而存在。”","id":337},{"type":"text","text":"“......”","id":338},{"type":"text","text":"“好。”","id":339},{"type":"dialog","id":340},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":341},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":342},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":343},{"type":"gridbg","id":344},{"type":"image","id":345},{"type":"charslot","id":346}],"characters":["阿斯卡纶","特雷西斯","巴别塔成员","？？？","细盐","凯尔希"]}